]])</span>\n| 56 || \u2014 || 72 || 43 || 44 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 27 || \u2014\n|\n* SNEP: Gold<ref name=\"SNEP\"/> \n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[All Stars (song)|All Stars]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Alma (Finnish singer)|Alma]])</span>\n| 2017\n| 11<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snepmusique.com/tops-semaine/top-singles-telecharges/?ye=2017&we=37|title=Le Top de la semaine : Top Singles T\u00e9l\u00e9charg\u00e9s \u2013 SNEP (Week 37, 2017)|publisher=[[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique]]|language=French|accessdate=19 September 2017}}{{Dead link|date=March 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> || \u2014 || 24 || 11 || 33 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 94 || 83 || \u2014\n|\n* SNEP: Platinum<ref name=\"SNEP\"/>\n* BEA: Gold<ref name=\"BEA\"/>\n* BVMI: Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\"/>\n* FIMI: Gold\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[My Love (Martin Solveig song)|My Love]]\"\n| 2018\n| 74 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 52 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[All Day and Night]]\"<br>{{small|(with [[Jax Jones]] and [[Madison Beer]])}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n| 95<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snepmusique.com/tops-semaine/top-singles-megafusion/?ye=2019&we=23|title=Le Top de la semaine : Top Singles (t\u00e9l\u00e9chargement + streaming) \u2013 SNEP (Week 23, 2019)|publisher=[[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique]]|language=French|accessdate=11 June 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816013405/http://www.snepmusique.com/tops-semaine/top-singles-megafusion/?ye=2019&we=23|archive-date=16 August 2019|url-status=dead}}</ref> || \u2014 || \u2014 || 52 || 85 || \u2014 || 79 || 85 || 10 || \u2014\n|\n* SNEP: Gold<ref name=\"SNEP\"/>\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n| ''[[Snacks (EP)|Snacks]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Thing for You]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with David Guetta)</span>\n| \u2014 || \