{"title_page": "List of programs broadcast by Nick Jr. (block)", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{multiple issues|\n{{refimprove|date=June 2012}}\n{{expert-subject|reason=it's very confusing to differentiate the various iterations of Nick Jr. by reading this article, without knowing the history|date=May 2013}}\n}}\nThe following is a '''list of programs broadcast by [[Nick Jr. (TV programming block)|Nick Jr.]]''', the [[Nickelodeon]] programming block broadcast from January 4, 1988, through January 30, 2009.<ref name=\"Nick Jr.(1996-1998) 10221997-1\">[https://web.archive.org/web/19971022011356/http://www.nick.com/nicktv/nicktv.cgi?g=8&d=0 Nickelodeon TV Times: October 22, 1997 (10:30-11:30 AM)]</ref> Afterwards, the [[Noggin (brand)#TV channel|Noggin]] network was rebranded as Nick Jr. on September 28.\n\n==Television shows==\nThe following is organized in ''[[alphabetical order]]''.\n\n=== Final television shows ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:70%;text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:20%;\" | Title\n! style=\"width:20%;\" | Premiere date\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Baby Einstein]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| February 1, 1997\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Blue's Clues]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| September 14, 1996\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[The Backyardigans]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| October 16, 2004\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Dora the Explorer]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| August 19, 2000\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Henry's World]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}||October 11, 2003\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Go, Diego, Go!]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| September 10, 2005\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Max & Ruby]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| October 26, 2002\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Ni Hao, Kai-Lan]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| February 9, 2008\n|-\n| style=\"text-ali