 Jr. (TV programming block)|Nick Jr.]]''', the [[Nickelodeon]] programming block broadcast from January 4, 1988, through January 30, 2009.<ref name=\"Nick Jr.(1996-1998) 10221997-1\">[https://web.archive.org/web/19971022011356/http://www.nick.com/nicktv/nicktv.cgi?g=8&d=0 Nickelodeon TV Times: October 22, 1997 (10:30-11:30 AM)]</ref> Afterwards, the [[Noggin (brand)#TV channel|Noggin]] network was rebranded as Nick Jr. on September 28.\n\n==Television shows==\nThe following is organized in ''[[alphabetical order]]''.\n\n=== Final television shows ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:70%;text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:20%;\" | Title\n! style=\"width:20%;\" | Premiere date\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[The Backyardigans]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| October 11, 2004\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Dora the Explorer]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| August 14, 2000\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Go, Diego, Go!]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| September 6, 2005\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Max & Ruby]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| October 21, 2002\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Ni Hao, Kai-Lan]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| February 7, 2008\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Olivia (TV series)|Olivia]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| January 26, 2009\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Wonder Pets!]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| March 3, 2006\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| August 28, 2006\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Yo Gabba Gabba!]]'' {{Ref|NoteA|a}}|| August 20, 2007\n|}\n\n== Former television shows ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:70%;text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:20%;\" | Title\n! style=\"width:20%;\" | Premiere date\n! style=\"width:30%;\" | Finale date\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" scope=\"row\" |''[[Adventures of the Lit