oye|Saturn Ramenskoye]]\n| 2004\n| \n| 119\n| 3\n|-\n| 6\n| [[Pyotr Bystrov]]\n| {{flagicon|RUS}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1979|7|15}}\n| [[FC Saturn Ramenskoye|Saturn Ramenskoye]]\n| 2006\n| \n| 63\n| 9\n|-\n| 7\n| [[Damian Gorawski]]\n| {{flagicon|POL}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1979|1|4}}\n| [[Wis\u0142a Krak\u00f3w]]\n| 2005\n| \n| 47\n| 1\n|-\n| 9\n| [[Sergei Semak]]\n| {{flagicon|RUS}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1976|2|27}}\n| [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]]\n| 2006\n| \n| 73\n| 15\n|-\n| 10\n| [[Maximiliano Moralez]]\n| {{flagicon|ARG}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1987|2|27}}\n| [[Racing Club de Avellaneda|Racing Club]]\n| 2007<ref name=\"Maximiliano Moralez\"/>\n| 2011<ref name=\"Maximiliano Moralez\"/>\n| 7\n| 0\n|-\n| 11\n| [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u010c\u00ed\u017eek]]\n| {{flagicon|CZE}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1978|11|27}}\n| [[FC Rubin Kazan|Rubin Kazan]]\n| 2006\n| \n| 60\n| 4\n|-\n| 17\n| [[Pavel Golyshev]]\n| {{flagicon|RUS}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1987|7|7}}\n| Youth Team\n| 2005\n| \n| 18\n| 2\n|-\n| 20\n| [[Aleksei Melyoshin]]\n| {{flagicon|RUS}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1976|1|30}}\n| [[FC Dynamo Saint Petersburg|Dynamo St.Petersburg]]\n| 2004\n| \n| 82\n| 11\n|-\n| 47\n| [[Artyom Varakin]]\n| {{flagicon|RUS}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1987|4|21}}\n| Youth Team\n| 2006\n| \n| 2\n| 0\n|-\n| 77\n| [[Stanislav Ivanov (footballer, born 1980)|Stanislav Ivanov]]\n| {{flagicon|MDA}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2007|11|11|1980|10|7}}\n| [[FC Sheriff Tiraspol|Sheriff Tiraspol]]\n| 2004\n| \n| 105\n| 6\n|-\n! colspan=\"11\"  style=\"background:#dcdcdc; text-align:center;\"| Forwards\n|-\n| 18\n| [[Maxi L\u00f3pez]]\n| {{flagicon|ARG}}\n| FW\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2006|11|26|1984|4|3}}\n| [[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n| 2007<ref name=\"Maxi L\u